Visiting Belgium

Not only the beers are the products that you can call economic advantages of Belgium. They know about the food and drinks a lot and everybody knows the Belgian cuisine will be able to satisfy a viscerally curious pub crawler. Excellent ones are bierges. Bierges is not considered to be beer capital but it is worth it and they got a large variety of beers that will delight everyone.

If you are interested in visiting the other places around the beer towns, you can visit Ghent with its medieval ramparts. You must not miss Brussels, the capital is an economic center of the world with a developed industry. You should stop by Bruges, one of the most authentic cities of the world where you will see romantic nightlife and you can swim in the sea during the European summer.
